TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup transformation on day dimension
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_DAY_DIM_SUFFIX

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT SUBSTR(to_char(DAY_DIMENSION.DAY_DATE,'DD/MM/YYYY'),1,2) as DAY_DATE , '1' as DUMMY FROM DAY_DIMENSION WHERE TRUNC(DAY_DATE)=TRUNC(SYSDATE)

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on SLBA_ITEM for getting DIV_DESC
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_ITEM_DIV

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Expression used for final calculation before loading to target
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_CALC_GRM

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on SLBA_ITEM
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_ITEM

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on Reference
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_REF_PROFIT_NUM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT Reference.Desc_1 as Desc_1, Reference.Reference_key as Reference_key, Reference.Reference_subkey_seq as Reference_subkey_seq FROM Reference with (nolock)

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on REFERENCE table for getting division_desc(generic)
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_REFERENCE_PROFIT

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT Reference.Desc_1 as Desc_1, UPPER(Reference.Reference_sub_key_2) as Reference_sub_key_2 FROM Reference with (nolock) WHERE Reference.Reference_key='HAAProfitMapping' and Reference.Desc_3 is NULL

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup for getting item id
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(SLBA_ITEM.ITEM_ID) as ITEM_ID, SLBA_ITEM.SKU as SKU FROM SLBA_ITEM where SLBA_ITEM.DIVISION_GROUP='haa' GROUP BY SLBA_ITEM.SKU, SLBA_ITEM.DIVISION_GROUP

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on XREFF_ACC table for getting cust_seq number
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_XREF_ACC

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT XRF_ACC.TS_DIV_CDE as TS_DIV_CDE, XRF_ACC.COUNTRY_CODE as COUNTRY_CODE, XRF_ACC.CUST_SEQ_NBR as CUST_SEQ_NBR, XRF_ACC.SOLDTO as SOLDTO FROM XRF_ACC XRF_ACC WHERE XRF_ACC.TS_DIV_CDE='HA'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on REFERENCE table for getting required field for business logic
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_REFERENCE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT Reference.Reference_sub_key_2 as Reference_sub_key_2, Reference.Desc_1 as Desc_1, Reference.Desc_2 as Desc_2, Reference.Desc_3 as Desc_3, Reference.Reference_sub_key_1 as Reference_sub_key_1 from Reference with (nolock) where Reference.reference_key='HAAMeasureMapping'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on SLBA_FACILITY
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_FACILITY_HBI

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_ID) as FACILITY_ID, SLBA_FACILITY.DIVISION_GROUP as DIVISION_GROUP FROM SLBA_FACILITY WHERE SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE IN ($$FACILITY_CODE) GROUP BY SLBA_FACILITY.DIVISION_GROUP

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on SLBA_ITEM for division group hbi
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_ITEM_HBI

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(SLBA_ITEM.ITEM_ID) as ITEM_ID, SLBA_ITEM.DIVISION_GROUP as DIVISION_GROUP FROM SLBA_ITEM WHERE SLBA_ITEM.STYLE_NUM in ($$STYLE_NUM) GROUP BY SLBA_ITEM.DIVISION_GROUP

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on DAY_DIMENSION for getting required date field
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_DAY_DIM

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on SLBA_FACILITY
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_FACILITY_HAA

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_ID) as FACILITY_ID, SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE as FACILITY_CODE, SLBA_FACILITY.DIVISION_GROUP as DIVISION_GROUP FROM SLBA_FACILITY GROUP BY SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE, SLBA_FACILITY.DIVISION_GROUP

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: All records from the Source
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_STG_HAA_SALES

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT STG_HAA_SALES.DIVISION_CODE, STG_HAA_SALES.INVOICE_FISCAL_YEAR, STG_HAA_SALES.INVOICE_FISCAL_PERIOD, STG_HAA_SALES.TRANSACTION_CATEGORY, STG_HAA_SALES.SALES_CATEGORY, STG_HAA_SALES.INVOICE_DATE, STG_HAA_SALES.SHIP_TO_CUSTOMER, STG_HAA_SALES.SHIP_FOR_CUSTOMER_ID, TRIM(STG_HAA_SALES.ORDER_NUMBER)||SUBSTR(TRIM(INVOICE_NUMBER),LEAST(LENGTH(INVOICE_NUMBER),20-LENGTH(STG_HAA_SALES.ORDER_NUMBER))*-1) as ORDER_NUMBER, STG_HAA_SALES.ORDERED_DATE, STG_HAA_SALES.TRANSACTION_SEQUENCE, STG_HAA_SALES.ITEM_ID, STG_HAA_SALES.LEVEL_1_ITEM_ID, STG_HAA_SALES.LEVEL_2_ITEM_ID, STG_HAA_SALES.SHIPPED_DATE, STG_HAA_SALES.INVOICE_DIVISION_CODE, STG_HAA_SALES.ADJUSTED_EXTENDED_COST_DOLLARS, STG_HAA_SALES.AS_OF_DATE, STG_HAA_SALES.CALCULATED_DELIVERY_DATE, STG_HAA_SALES.CHARGE_ALLOWANCE_CODE, STG_HAA_SALES.CHARGE_ALLOWANCE_PREFIX, STG_HAA_SALES.CHARGE_ALLOWANCE_PREFIX_DESC, STG_HAA_SALES.CODE_PRODUCT_INDICATOR, STG_HAA_SALES.DAYS_SHIP_EARLY_OR_LATE, STG_HAA_SALES.DISTRIBUTION_CTR_FACILITY_ID, STG_HAA_SALES.DIVISION_GROUP, STG_HAA_SALES.INVOICE_DOLLARS, STG_HAA_SALES.INVOICED_DOZENS, STG_HAA_SALES.EVENT_CODE, STG_HAA_SALES.EXTENDED_COST_DOLLARS, STG_HAA_SALES.MEASURE_NAME, STG_HAA_SALES.MEASURE_TYPE, STG_HAA_SALES.INVOICE_DATE_FISCAL_WEEK, STG_HAA_SALES.INVOICED_UNITS, STG_HAA_SALES.GL_SALES_ACCOUNT_NUMBER, STG_HAA_SALES.GL_COST_ACCOUNT, STG_HAA_SALES.GROSS_MARGIN_IND, STG_HAA_SALES.GROSS_PROFIT_DOLLARS, STG_HAA_SALES.INVOICE_NUMBER, STG_HAA_SALES.INVOICED_QUALITY, STG_HAA_SALES.LATE_INDICATOR, STG_HAA_SALES.LEVEL_1_DIVISION_CODE, STG_HAA_SALES.LEVEL_2_DIVISION_CODE, STG_HAA_SALES.PURCHASE_ORDER_NUMBER, STG_HAA_SALES.REQUESTED_SHIP_DATE, STG_HAA_SALES.CUST_SOLD_TO_ACCOUNT_NUMBER, STG_HAA_SALES.ORDER_TYPE, STG_HAA_SALES.PURCHASE_ORDER_TYPE, STG_HAA_SALES.RETURN_CODE, STG_HAA_SALES.SELLING_UNITS, STG_HAA_SALES.DATE_OF_TRANSACTION, STG_HAA_SALES.TRANSACTION_USERID, STG_HAA_SALES.CALL_IN_DATE, STG_HAA_SALES.RELEASED_GARMENTS, STG_HAA_SALES.RELEASED_UNITS, STG_HAA_SALES.DEMAND_GARMENTS, STG_HAA_SALES.BACK_ORDER_INDICATOR, STG_HAA_SALES.CANCEL_BY_DATE, STG_HAA_SALES.GOOD_SERVICE_DATE, STG_HAA_SALES.ORIGINAL_ORDER_DOLLARS, STG_HAA_SALES.ORIGINAL_ORDER_GARMENTS, STG_HAA_SALES.SALES_MEASURE_NAME, STG_HAA_SALES.COST_MEASURE_NAME, STG_HAA_SALES.INVOICE_AMT_IN_LOCAL_CURRENCY, STG_HAA_SALES.COST_IN_LOCAL_CURRENCY_AMOUNT, STG_HAA_SALES.SAP_CUSTOMER_SOLD_TO_NUMBER, STG_HAA_SALES.SAP_CUSTOMER_SHIP_TO_NUMBER, STG_HAA_SALES.SAP_MATERIAL_ID, STG_HAA_SALES.SAP_GRID_VALUE, STG_HAA_SALES.SAP_PROFIT_CENTER, STG_HAA_SALES.SAP_PREPACK_INDICATOR, STG_HAA_SALES.PREVIOUS_YEAR_COSTS, STG_HAA_SALES.PREVIOUS_YEAR_PRICE, STG_HAA_SALES.GL_COMPANY, STG_HAA_SALES.GL_ACCOUNTING_UNIT_1, STG_HAA_SALES.GL_ACCOUNTING_UNIT_2, STG_HAA_SALES.GL_ACCOUNT_CATEGORY, STG_HAA_SALES.GL_CURRENCY_CODE, STG_HAA_SALES.SALES_RESPONSIBILITY, STG_HAA_SALES.CURRENCY_CODE, STG_HAA_SALES.UPDATE_USERID, STG_HAA_SALES.UPDATE_TIMESTAMP FROM STG_HAA_SALES ORDER BY STG_HAA_SALES.ORDER_NUMBER, STG_HAA_SALES.INVOICE_DATE
